# ─── edge-proxy/.env — SECRETS ONLY (gitignored; chmod 600) ───────────────────
# All non-secret configuration (ports, domains, TLS mode, images, log level)
# is render-time: edit ciu-stack/ciu.toml.j2 and run scripts/render.sh, or use
# scripts/install.sh.  This file is only read in tls.mode = "acme-dns", where
# it is passed to the traefik container via env_file for the lego DNS provider.
#
# Provider credential variable names: https://go-acme.github.io/lego/dns/
#
# Cloudflare (scoped API token with Zone:Read + DNS:Edit):
# CF_DNS_API_TOKEN=...
#
# Hetzner DNS:
# HETZNER_API_KEY=...
#
# AWS Route 53:
# AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=...
# AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=...
# AWS_REGION=...
#
# deSEC (free, supports CNAME delegation of _acme-challenge):
# DESEC_TOKEN=...
